1
00:01:12,759 --> 00:01:14,080
We were just passing by

2
00:01:14,639 --> 00:01:16,000
and heard quite a commotion inside.

3
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:19,519
Who was it that spoke of evident filial piety?

4
00:01:25,320 --> 00:01:26,239
Your Majesty,

5
00:01:26,679 --> 00:01:28,600
Consort Su mentioned to this servant...

6
00:01:29,359 --> 00:01:32,399
that the Empress Dowager once praised the Late Empress in tender-leaf yellow,

7
00:01:32,399 --> 00:01:33,760
calling it dignified and elegant.

8
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,079
That is true.

9
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,239
Today, Noble Consort Meng and...

10
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:40,079
Consort Su...

11
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,000
are both wearing this color.

12
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,200
It is a gesture of respect for the Empress Dowager...

13
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,560
and remembrance of the Late Empress.

14
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,520
Your Majesty,

15
00:01:46,119 --> 00:01:47,320
it is not as she says.

16
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,520
The Empress Dowager interfered in politics...

17
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,439
and was unworthy of her position.

18
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:51,240
Your servant holds no respect for her whatsoever.

19
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,520
Then it seems...

20
00:01:53,119 --> 00:01:55,039
you have no respect for the Empress Dowager,

21
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:57,840
nor any remembrance for the Late Empress.

22
00:02:04,039 --> 00:02:04,840
Your servant...

23
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:07,320
Your servant did not mean that either.

24
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,840
Then what did you mean?

25
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:09,920
I...

26
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,320
Your Majesty,

27
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:16,319
your servant is indeed mourning the Late Empress.

28
00:02:17,599 --> 00:02:18,359
Then...

29
00:02:19,599 --> 00:02:20,760
what of the Empress Dowager?

30
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,760
Your Majesty is wise.

31
00:02:27,359 --> 00:02:29,640
The Empress Dowager's merits and faults are for Your Majesty to judge.

32
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,599
Consort Su dares not discuss them rashly.

33
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,719
She merely observes the etiquette of a consort...

34
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:34,760
and maintains a heart of filial piety.

35
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:40,840
Your Majesty,

36
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:42,879
today is the Empress Dowager's posthumous birthday.

37
00:02:43,359 --> 00:02:45,959
Noble Consort Meng and Consort Su speak only of filial piety.

38
00:02:46,719 --> 00:02:48,040
The harem must not interfere in politics;

39
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:50,400
the imperial consorts keep this firmly in mind.

40
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:03,760
You...

41
00:03:04,159 --> 00:03:05,079
Raise your head.

42
00:03:10,359 --> 00:03:11,799
You are quite bold.

43
00:03:12,319 --> 00:03:14,519
You dare protect your master like this before Us?

44
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,079
This servant is terrified.

45
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:20,080
This servant protects Your Majesty's divine prestige...

46
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,639
your benevolence, filial piety, and generosity...

47
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:22,719
and your virtue that wins over the masses.

48
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,599
What a sharp tongue.

49
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,120
You are even flattering Us now.

50
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,719
Enough.

51
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:34,000
The Empress Dowager's burial in the Imperial Tombs was Our decree...

52
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,240
and the Late Empress's dying wish.

53
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:39,680
Do not discuss it rashly in the future.

54
00:03:40,919 --> 00:03:42,400
Your servant obeys the decree.

55
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:47,360
He actually buried the Empress Dowager in the Imperial Tombs,

56
00:03:47,879 --> 00:03:49,759
and claimed it was my dying wish.

57
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,560
You have done a fine job.

58
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:54,520
Causing This one to lose all face.

59
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,719
My Lady, this fabric was... Feng Qing...

60
00:03:56,719 --> 00:03:58,039
it was Feng Qing who prepared it.

61
00:03:58,039 --> 00:03:59,960
She knows people at the Bureau of Imperial Attire, so...

62
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,879
Sister Bi Hen,

63
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:03,120
I only embroidered the patterns on this dress.

64
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,719
It was clearly you who had the Bureau of Imperial Attire prepare it.

65
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,719
My Lady,

66
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:07,520
many servants can testify to this.

67
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,800
This servant heard Sister Bi Hen say with her own mouth...

68
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,159
that this tender-leaf yellow palace dress...

69
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,439
was specially prepared by her.

70
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:15,199
This servant... this servant heard it too.

71
00:04:17,159 --> 00:04:18,080
You witch!

72
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:19,639
You dare to set me up?

73
00:04:21,919 --> 00:04:23,360
When have I ever suffered such humiliation?

74
00:04:24,159 --> 00:04:25,360
Keeping your worthless life...

75
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:27,240
how can it quell the hatred in my heart?

76
00:04:27,599 --> 00:04:28,319
Guards!

77
00:04:28,479 --> 00:04:30,319
Get this lowly servant out of my sight.

78
00:04:30,719 --> 00:04:31,520
My Lady!

79
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,680
My Lady, spare me! My Lady!

80
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,360
My Lady!

81
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,759
My Lady, spare me!

82
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,439
My Lady!

83
00:04:58,919 --> 00:04:59,639
My Lady!

84
00:05:00,039 --> 00:05:01,479
Even if Sister Bi Hen is at fault,

85
00:05:01,719 --> 00:05:03,800
she blundered only out of loyalty.

86
00:05:07,960 --> 00:05:09,919
If she dies, you can replace her.

87
00:05:10,599 --> 00:05:12,159
Yet now you speak for her.

88
00:05:12,599 --> 00:05:14,120
It seems you are not only loyal...

89
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,840
but also lack ambition.

90
00:05:16,639 --> 00:05:18,360
This servant only seeks to serve My Lady.

91
00:05:23,639 --> 00:05:25,280
Remember well the taste of today.

92
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:26,879
If there is another mistake,

93
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:28,920
do not blame me for showing no mercy.

94
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,360
Thank you, My Lady.

95
00:05:36,319 --> 00:05:37,879
Thank you, Sister Feng Qing.

96
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,720
Today, Feng Qing loyally protected her master.

97
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:42,879
Reward her heavily.

98
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,120
In the future, she may serve as a personal attendant.

99
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:22,759
Consort Su

100
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:25,439
In that great fire,

101
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:28,160
what role did you actually play?

102
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,639
My Lady, are you feeling unwell somewhere?

103
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:40,600
Thinking back on today's events, I still feel shaken.

104
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:42,759
Imperial Noble Consort Wan is just a paper tiger.

105
00:06:42,879 --> 00:06:44,560
She cannot handle Noble Consort Meng at all.

106
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,000
Please calm down, My Lady.

107
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,480
Within the palace, no flower blooms for a hundred days.

108
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,720
If Noble Consort Meng stumbles one day,

109
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,519
everyone will push the wall as it falls.

110
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,560
That is true.

111
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:57,240
The Late Empress was a model for the realm,

112
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:59,360
yet didn't she also turn to ash in a fire?

113
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:01,639
There are no evergreens in this harem.

114
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,600
If the Late Empress were still alive,

115
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,199
Noble Consort Meng would not dare to be so impudent.

116
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:14,439
The Late Empress was very strict in the past,

117
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:16,600
but she was always even-handed in her dealings.

118
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,720
When she was in the harem,

119
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,160
Consort Cao and Noble Consort Meng were actually well-behaved.

120
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:24,120
My Lady, you were startled today.

121
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,319
I heard

122
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:29,160
that you have a type of incense from the Western Regions here.

123
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,839
It is especially good for calming the mind and spirit.

124
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:32,680
Why don't this servant find it and light it

125
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,920
to help you relax?

126
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,879
Western Regions Calming Incense?

127
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:40,680
Very well.

128
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:43,040
Go take it from the shelf and light it.

129
00:08:03,759 --> 00:08:05,240
It is the very incense from the mourning hall that day.

130
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:08,560
This Western Regions Calming Incense

131
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,279
is vastly different from ordinary incense.

132
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:13,399
It must be extremely rare and precious, right?

133
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:16,120
Others may view it as a treasure,

134
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:17,360
but for my Su family,

135
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,839
it is just a common item used to bribe the various palaces.

136
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,800
I award the remaining half-packet to you.

137
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,040
Thank you for your grace, My Lady.

138
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,199
You may withdraw.

139
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:31,680
She seems to bear no ill will toward this one.

140
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:33,959
This calming incense

141
00:08:34,160 --> 00:08:35,839
was also casually gifted to others by her.

142
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,600
It seems I must find another way to test her.

143
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:51,560
Sister, you are now My Lady's personal maid.

144
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:53,160
Let us do these chores.

145
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:55,079
Good sister,

146
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,040
when you served My Lady yesterday,

147
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,120
did she mention me?

148
00:08:59,959 --> 00:09:01,800
My Lady was just angered by Noble Consort Meng,

149
00:09:01,959 --> 00:09:03,000
so she took it out on you, Sister.

150
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,720
She also said,

151
00:09:05,319 --> 00:09:06,839
"If the Late Empress were still here,

152
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,439
how could Noble Consort Meng be so impudent?"

153
00:09:08,839 --> 00:09:10,639
My Lady always wanted to seek protection

154
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:11,759
from the Late Empress.

155
00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:13,879
She even specially crafted a solid gold ruyi scepter,

156
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:16,000
intending to present it on the Empress's birthday.

157
00:09:16,319 --> 00:09:17,399
But who would have thought,

158
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:18,759
the Empress would pass away so unexpectedly.

159
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,199
This one's birthday had not yet arrived,

160
00:09:21,199 --> 00:09:22,720
yet she had already prepared a birthday gift.

161
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,959
The person who engineered the fire

162
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,480
should not be Consort Su.

163
00:09:30,079 --> 00:09:31,199
Sister, you have suffered.

164
00:09:31,439 --> 00:09:32,439
I thought

165
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:34,160
My Lady treated you differently,

166
00:09:34,439 --> 00:09:35,879
that it wouldn't be like with Wen Tang.

167
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:39,120
How do you know about Wen Tang too?

168
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,480
It was her bad luck.

169
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,480
When combing My Lady's hair,

170
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,919
she accidentally pulled out some strands.

171
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,759
In a fit of rage, My Lady

172
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:47,320
stabbed a hairpin into her neck.

173
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:51,000
Are the lives of servants worth no more than grass?

174
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,120
Isn't that the truth?

175
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,279
We have to keep the masters happy.

176
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,000
How about this,

177
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,200
I will go pick some crabapple flowers

178
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,240
to make rouge for My Lady.

179
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,639
You go pick some peach blossoms too, alright?

180
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,120
I'm off then.

181
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,879
Wen Tang died a tragic death,

182
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,240
just because she combed out a few strands of her hair.

183
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:10,080
Su Dai, you treat human life like grass.

184
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:12,919
This one will surely seek justice for Wen Tang.

185
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,840
Halt.

186
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,720
This servant greets Your Majesty.

187
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,639
Blessings to Your Majesty.

188
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,120
We remember you.

189
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,360
The loyal one who spoke up for Consort Su.

190
00:10:38,720 --> 00:10:39,519
What are you doing here?

191
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:42,519
This servant came to collect peach petals for rouge.

192
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,440
How dare you!

193
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:45,000
Your Majesty has decreed...

194
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:46,840
...picking from this peach tree is forbidden.

195
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,879
Violators receive thirty strokes of the cane.

196
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:52,000
Let's see what you have to say this time.

197
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,639
This servant could never bear to pick flowers.

198
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,600
I came here only to wait for the wind.

199
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:58,159
To gather some fallen petals.

200
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,960
You actually still have an excuse.

201
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:03,519
Sophistry.

202
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:06,080
Flowers bloom and fade in their own time.

203
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,679
The beginning and end of a bond is beyond our control.

204
00:11:08,039 --> 00:11:09,159
This servant does not pick flowers...

205
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,440
...because I cannot bear to disturb...

206
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,879
...this already fleeting blooming season.

207
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,799
Do not pick it.

208
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,480
Flowers bloom and fade in their own time.

209
00:11:26,039 --> 00:11:27,320
Why must you pluck them?

210
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,279
When the wind blows,

211
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,879
the fallen petals are just as beautiful.

212
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:40,559
You may withdraw.

213
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,039
This servant takes her leave.

214
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:58,279
The beginning and end of a bond is beyond our control.

215
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,919
Could it be that our bond ends here?

216
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:02,759
This endgame...

217
00:12:03,879 --> 00:12:05,840
Is there no one left to solve it for We?

218
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:11,720
Excuse me, sister.

219
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,960
Is Feng Qing here?

220
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,279
Feng Qing has gone to serve as a maid in Consort Su's palace.

221
00:12:17,519 --> 00:12:18,320
What?

222
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:20,200
She went to Yongfu Palace.

223
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:23,639
My Lord, if you have urgent business with Feng Qing...

224
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,039
I can pass on a message for you.

225
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:29,360
She seems to have a close relationship with Feng Qing.

226
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:32,120
The matter Feng Qing asked you to investigate...

227
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:33,159
Is there a result?

228
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,600
She hasn't asked me to investigate anything.

229
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,200
You are lying.

230
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,399
What do you know?

231
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,279
I... I don't know anything.

232
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:47,159
Don't come any closer.

233
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,240
Speak.

234
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,919
Tell me everything you know.

235
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,759
Lord Gu, how imposing you are.

236
00:12:56,519 --> 00:12:57,679
Bullying a weak woman.

237
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,279
Without a shred of grace or dignity.

238
00:13:02,159 --> 00:13:03,440
What is this scar about?

239
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,120
It seems when you asked me for medicine,

240
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:06,200
you were hiding something from me.

241
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,440
Have you considered the consequences?

242
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:09,720
I can explain this matter.

243
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,519
Lord Gu, do not involve the innocent.

244
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,759
Wen Xin, you go out first.

245
00:13:16,559 --> 00:13:18,399
Tell me, what have you found out?

246
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,840
He questions so unscrupulously.

247
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,200
If he learns the truth,

248
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,919
I fear he will do something even more dangerous.

249
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:27,480
I haven't found anything yet.

250
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,440
Nothing?

251
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,519
Please believe me, Lord Gu.

252
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:33,799
Give me a little more time.

253
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:34,879
You have already wasted one chance

254
00:13:34,879 --> 00:13:36,240
to make me trust you.

255
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,879
If you find nothing,

256
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,679
her life will pay the price.

257
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,840
A healer's blade...

258
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:43,120
...should protect the people.

259
00:13:43,720 --> 00:13:45,159
Lord Gu, as a healer,

260
00:13:45,399 --> 00:13:46,600
how can you use a blade meant for saving lives

261
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,759
to harm people?

262
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:55,720
A healer's blade...

263
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:57,000
...should protect the people.

264
00:13:57,399 --> 00:13:59,279
A-Xuan, remember this.

265
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:01,600
A healer holds a blade to save people,

266
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,840
not to harm them.

267
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:08,120
I want results within three days.

268
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,240
Otherwise,

269
00:14:09,799 --> 00:14:11,639
I will no longer leave any room

270
00:14:11,759 --> 00:14:12,919
for someone unworthy of trust.

271
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:21,879
I'm sorry.

272
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,279
I got you involved.

273
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,159
It's okay.

274
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,679
I wasn't really hurt.

275
00:14:27,399 --> 00:14:28,919
How did you provoke him?

276
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,399
It's a long story.

277
00:14:33,039 --> 00:14:34,039
If you meet him in the future,

278
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:35,159
you must stay far away.

279
00:14:37,159 --> 00:14:39,440
Feng Qing, you came to find me so late.

280
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,600
Is something the matter?

281
00:14:43,399 --> 00:14:45,120
Regarding your sister Wen Tang...

282
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,080
I have asked around for you.

283
00:14:50,039 --> 00:14:51,840
Just for messing up a few strands of hair,

284
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,639
she had to pay with her life.

285
00:14:54,399 --> 00:14:55,919
She was only sixteen.

286
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,440
Su Dai has a violent temper.

287
00:14:59,720 --> 00:15:01,399
She takes her anger out on others at the slightest provocation.

288
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:03,720
I will make her pay the price.

289
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:04,639
She will reap what she sows.

290
00:15:05,159 --> 00:15:06,600
Thank you for helping me so much.

291
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:10,000
From now on, no matter what happens,

292
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:11,039
I will listen to you.

293
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,240
About the matching outfits...

294
00:15:21,399 --> 00:15:22,559
His Majesty didn't even pursue it.

295
00:15:22,559 --> 00:15:24,519
On what grounds did Noble Consort Meng withdraw my name tag?

296
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:25,879
His Majesty is busy with state affairs.

297
00:15:25,879 --> 00:15:28,120
I tried so hard last month to get him to stay the night once.

298
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,320
Now with this situation,

299
00:15:29,320 --> 00:15:30,679
His Majesty will remember me even less.

300
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:33,879
My Lady, do not be anxious.

301
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,639
This servant has a plan.

302
00:15:36,799 --> 00:15:38,879
It can win His Majesty's favor for you, My Lady.

303
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,480
What method do you have?

304
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:42,679
In this servant's opinion,

305
00:15:43,639 --> 00:15:44,559
you might as well

306
00:15:45,039 --> 00:15:46,399
cater to his preferences.
